articles.author: Tara Subramaniam
articles.title: Australian woman charged with murder over suspected death cap mushroom poisonings - CNN
articles.description: Australian police arrested a 49-year-old woman Thursday in connection with a fatal poisoning in late July, which involved suspected death cap mushrooms and killed three people.
articles.content:
Australian police have brought murder charges against a woman who served a lunch earlier this year that led to the deaths of three people from suspected death cap mushroom poisoning.
